* Iron Raptor moved her neck a bit to get use to Prowls arms around it, 
feeling his muscles tighten as she runs.
She turned her head a bit to hear Prowls words as he spoke, keeping pace and 
knowing that the Ark was only a few moments away.*

" She runs on her own power, she should still function. If not then I can 
simply take a sample of her programming that's lefy and she can reconfigure 
herself. Either way she'll tell me what's going on with this walking 
nightmare I'm wearing..."

* And with that she came over a slow rise, and there in the distance was the 
remains of the ark, far worse then Iron Raptor had thought.*

" How did this happen........"

* Her voice could barely be heard as she simply stoon on the rise, eyes side 
and almost unable to believe what she saw...*
